YOU WILL NEED TO RUN THIS ON A KALI BOX

REQUIRED PACKAGES 
- scapy (install with pip)

HOW TO RUN
- Openn a terminal
- type "python3 mongoose.py"
- Follow the prompts based on how you want to run the program

INPUTS
- Run program in random mode or not: "Y" or "N"
- Target machine IP address: eg. 192.168.10.25
- Target port: eg. 80
- Source port: eg. 1234 
- If running in percise mode, you will need to specifiy a source IP address: eg. 154.20.70.5
